channel.title: [PI] Server keeps opening and closing
channel.description:
was following this dungeonering tutorial here: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,498306.0.html
I compiled with no errors, went to run my server, and it kept opening and closing. I managed to get a screenshot but couldn't post it because eventually I had to restart my computer. It mentioned something like cannot find main class server.server or something around there. could anyone tell me what I did wrong?
